{% macro summary() -%}
<section id="about" class="home-section text-center bg-gray">
  <div class="heading-about marginbot-50">
	<div class="container">
	  <div class="row">
		<div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2">

		  <div class="section-heading">
			<h2>What do we do?</h2>
			<p>At the beginning of each year, the American Mock Trial Association releases<a href="http://www.collegemocktrial.org/resources/case-materials/case-updates/criminal-case-preview"> new case materials</a>.
              We spend the most of the year debating the same case
              with other schools around the country, then <a href="http://www.collegemocktrial.org/MEMO%20RE%202015%20NCT%20Case%20Procedures%20-%20FINAL.pdf">switch it up</a> with a new case at the National Championship Tournament in April.</p>
		  </div>

		</div>
	  </div>
	</div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-3 col-md-3">

        <div class="service-box">
		  <div class="service-icon">
			<i class="fa fa-legal fa-3x"></i>
		  </div>
		  <div class="service-desc">
			<h5>Debate</h5>
			<p>Join the team as an attorney to hone your legal
			skills. Attorneys win points for the team by making
			speeches, examining witnesses, and arguing objections. </p>
		  </div>
        </div>

      </div>
	  <div class="col-sm-3 col-md-3">

        <div class="service-box">
		  <div class="service-icon">
